y Thục kỹ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ti%E1%BB%83u-h%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-chu-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-2mMZILOCuzgaEX--NzW2vg">Tiểu hàn thực chu trung tác - 小寒食舟中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Kh%E1%BB%9Fi/T%E1%BB%91ng-chinh-nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-se0QQTBr2Ub2n6CbNARdOg">Tống chinh nhạn - 送征雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Kh%E1%BB%9Fi/author-Lmk1srGEtNuIi0hYAVvAPA">Tiền Khởi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ADnh/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-rqE-l8ZaTcmi0NBQ5qJUdA">Vô đề kỳ 1 - 無題其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ADnh/author-ZSJGdqhomRPBVjiE5QU4sQ">Trần Phương Bính</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-Wvbt6J7ouRO2HwyEs7xM9A">Xuân từ - 春詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
